value: I'm not sure what your game is, having me wear this outfit... But I'm delighted to play.
Don't get yourself too riled up. These clothes are just on loan.
The people of Múspell can be pretty hot-blooded... But play your cards right, and they'll be wrapped around your little finger.
Oh, relax. I may have a new set of threads, but I'm the same Niles you know and love. Don't make me prove it.
Ahh... There's nothing so sublime as watching someone's happiness turn to horror as flames consume all they hold dear...
La luna di Múspell riflette il rosso vivo delle sue fiamme?
Lasciamo che le nostre anime ardano di passione.
